description:
This is my new channel trailer. There is no new material in here, just clips from my videos that illustrate what my channel is all about.

Please feel free to mirror it or pass it on if you'd like other people to get to know this channel. Thanks.

The charity I strongly endorse is called Health in Harmony. 
   Listen to my radio report here: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b08h...
   Or read about it here: https://psmag.com/social-justice/save...... for an explanation of their work.

  You can make a donation by bank transfer here…
https://healthinharmony.org/donate/

Or by Paypal here:
https://www.paypal.com/fundraiser/112...

Thanks -- Your generous donations are what keep this channel going.
